Aah!

12
00:01:23,073 --> 00:01:26,304
Aah!

13
00:01:29,946 --> 00:01:32,574
You're going to dislocate your shoulder.

14
00:01:32,682 --> 00:01:34,582
Screw you!

15
00:01:43,426 --> 00:01:45,656
You religious or something?

16
00:01:46,963 --> 00:01:48,487
I try.

17
00:01:59,976 --> 00:02:00,908
Smoke?

18
00:02:25,969 --> 00:02:27,766
You got a name?

19
00:02:27,871 --> 00:02:28,838
Annie.

20
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:33,234
Is that a street name?

21
00:02:33,343 --> 00:02:34,833
You been in before?

22
00:02:36,346 --> 00:02:38,576
Once or twice.

23
00:02:38,682 --> 00:02:39,649
For what?

24
00:02:41,685 --> 00:02:45,121
Oh, this time, for blocking the federal building,

25
00:02:45,222 --> 00:02:46,917
protesting the hydrogen bomb.

26
00:02:47,023 --> 00:02:48,456
M-making...

27
00:02:48,558 --> 00:02:51,254
[retching]

28
00:02:51,361 --> 00:02:52,259
Oh, God.

29
00:02:52,362 --> 00:02:54,353
[vomits]

30
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:59,794
Oh, I made a mess of your shoes.

31
00:02:59,903 --> 00:03:01,495
They're as old as I am.

32
00:03:06,109 --> 00:03:10,443
I once was lost

33
00:03:10,547 --> 00:03:12,378
but now

34
00:03:12,482 --> 00:03:13,972
I'm found

35
00:03:16,052 --> 00:03:18,520
I was blind

36
00:03:18,622 --> 00:03:23,389
but now

37
00:03:23,493 --> 00:03:25,393
I see

38
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:31,191
Who are you?

39
00:03:31,301 --> 00:03:35,761
(singing) Amazing

40
00:03:35,872 --> 00:03:37,840
grace

41
00:03:37,941 --> 00:03:40,842
how sweet

42
00:03:40,944 --> 00:03:43,105
the sound

43
00:03:44,347 --> 00:03:47,248
that saved

44
00:03:47,350 --> 00:03:50,444
a wretch

45
00:03:50,553 --> 00:03:53,852
like me

46
